{{define "title"}}URY Elections - Home{{end}}
{{define "content"}}
    <div class="container prevent-select">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-content">
                <p>I am afraid this part is just the welcome section.
                    If you are an administrator, then you'll know where to go, but if you're a voter,
                    then you will be emailed a link that will take you to the correct election.</p>
                {{if .AllowRegistration}}
                    <br>
                    <p>
                        If you have not registered to vote, then use the link below to sign up to vote.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <p>
                        <a class="button is-link" href="/registration">Register to vote!</a>
                    </p>
                {{end}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{{end}}
